<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui">
	<ui:style field="first">

	</ui:style>
	<ui:style field="second" src="styles/styles.css"/>
	<ui:style field="third" src="styles/bootstrap.css"/>
	<ui:style field="forth" src="styles/bootstrap-theme.min.css"/>
	<g:HTMLPanel>
		<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	      <tr>
	        <td align="right" valign="middle">
	        	<p class="lead main-text" style="font-size:26px; text-align:right">Cargar un plan de estudio</p>
            </td>
	        <td width="100" rowspan="2">
            	<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center"><table width="2" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="1" height="170" bgcolor="#666666"></td>
                      </tr>
                    </table></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td  align="center" valign="bottom" class="lead main-text" style="font-size:26px; text-align:center">ó</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center"><table width="2" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="1" height="170" bgcolor="#666666"></td>
                      </tr>
                    </table></td>
                  </tr>
                </table>            
            </td>
	        <td align="left" valign="middle">
            	<p class="lead main-text" style="font-size:26px; text-align:left">Cargar <strong>MI</strong> plan de estudio</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
	      <tr>
	        <td width="45%" align="right" valign="middle">
              	<g:ListBox ui:field="listBoxCreate" addStyleNames="{second.textboxCreate} {third.lead} "></g:ListBox><br></br>
              	<p><g:Button ui:field="continueDefaultButton" addStyleNames="{third.btn} {third.btn-default}">Cargar plan de Ingeniería de Sistemas</g:Button></p>
            </td>
	        <td width="45%" height="400" align="left" valign="middle" style="font-size:20px; text-align:left" class="lead main-text">
            <ol>
	          <li>Ve al <strong>SIA</strong> y luego a <strong>Historia Académica</strong></li>
	          <li><kbd>ctrl + A</kbd> o <kbd>ctrl + E</kbd>*</li>
	          <li><kbd>ctrl + C</kbd></li>
	          <li>Pégalo aquí <kbd>ctrl + V</kbd> <img src="/images/favicon.png" width="16" height="16"/></li>
	          </ol>
              <p>
              	<g:TextBox ui:field="textBoxCreate" styleName="{second.textboxCreate}"></g:TextBox>
              </p>
              <p><g:Button ui:field="continueButton" addStyleNames="{third.btn} {third.btn-default}">Continuar</g:Button>  <g:Button ui:field="resetButton" addStyleNames="{third.btn} {third.btn-default}">Reiniciar</g:Button></p>
              <br/><p class="lead main-text" style="font-size:14px; text-align:left">*O solamente copia desde el título &quot;Mi historia académica&quot; hasta comenzar las palabras &quot;Resumen académico&quot;</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
	</g:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 